  m_Text: 'Snap Points can be attached to just about anything. Make holsters, wall
    mounts, or entire inventory systems.


    You can  automatically scale objects
    inside of a Snap Point. For example, when an object is snapped to this block,
    they are scaled to 50%.


    You can even put backpacks inside of backpacks!'
